WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:03.149
We did it, family. We stopped

00:00:03.149 --> 00:00:03.159
him—the

00:00:03.159 --> 00:00:05.590
man I told you I saw in the

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.510
spirit who was going to try to do

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.669
something at Trump's rally. There were two

00:00:09.679 --> 00:00:11.589
different articles sent to me by two

00:00:11.599 --> 00:00:14.869
different viewers telling me, "Hey Brandon,

00:00:14.879 --> 00:00:17.349
look what happened at Coachella."I told

00:00:17.359 --> 00:00:19.550
everybody we must pray for Coachella

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:21.470
because there's an attempt on Trump that

00:00:21.470 --> 00:00:21.480
was

00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:23.750
going to be there, and I told everybody,

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:25.189
"Hey, they're going to try to shoot people

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:26.790
in the crowd. This is going to be a big

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:30.830
deal; we have to pray against

00:00:30.830 --> 00:00:30.840
this."Well,

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:32.670
nothing was said all

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:33.709
day

00:00:33.719 --> 00:00:36.310
yesterday about any kind of anything

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:38.549
in the news. Well, today I'm getting all

00:00:38.559 --> 00:00:41.069
these articles from people telling me,

00:00:41.079 --> 00:00:44.110
"Brandon, look, he was

00:00:44.110 --> 00:00:44.120
stopped."He

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:47.790
had a fake security pass, a fake

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:50.110
press pass; he had all kinds of things to

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:53.150
try to get inside the event to try to

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.950
get close to Trump. So I just want to

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:59.430
give all the glory to God, for He shows

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:00.830
the

00:01:00.830 --> 00:01:00.840
watchman

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:03.590
on the wall to warn them to pray

00:01:03.590 --> 00:01:03.600
on

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.950
behalf of whatever He needs them to be

00:01:05.960 --> 00:01:08.830
praying for. We are making a

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:10.830
difference, and I just want to encourage

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:13.710
you all.

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:15.950
Thank you for coming and praying with

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:18.390
me and my little prayer group

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:22.149
here. I am so excited, I'm

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:24.030
speechless. I'm just like, "Wow, thank you,

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:25.910
Lord. Look at what we're

00:01:25.910 --> 00:01:25.920
doing."We're

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:27.950
making a difference, and I just want to

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:29.710
encourage you to keep going. We have to pray; there

00:01:29.710 --> 00:01:29.720
are

00:01:29.720 --> 00:01:31.350
still things we have to pray

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:33.670
about clear up until after the

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.749
election. So we're going to be making

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.469
these prayer videos. Here's our prayer

00:01:37.479 --> 00:01:40.710
video today. So God bless you all and

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:42.429
thank you. And then they had the big

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:45.230
prayer thing in Washington, D.C.,

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:47.149
and nothing happened there. We interceded

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:49.510
for that. I was praying for protection

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:51.950
over the people, that no secret enemy

00:01:51.960 --> 00:01:54.109
attacks or anything would happen during the big prayer

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:57.310
thing with Jonathan Cahn.

00:01:57.310 --> 00:01:57.320
From

00:01:57.320 --> 00:02:00.389
what I saw, nothing evil happened at all

00:02:00.399 --> 00:02:02.870
there, and there were probably 20,000

00:02:02.870 --> 00:02:02.880
to

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.709
30,000 people there. It was

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:07.149
a lot of people in the camera shot

00:02:07.149 --> 00:02:07.159
who

00:02:07.159 --> 00:02:09.469
were interceding, taking communion,

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:11.150
and praying for this nation, and they

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:13.949
were worshiping Jesus. You could feel the

00:02:13.959 --> 00:02:16.030
presence of the Lord tangibly when I was

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:18.430
watching it. If you didn't watch that, go

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:20.550
back and watch that again. I believe they

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:23.110
probably have a replay on Jonathan

00:02:23.110 --> 00:02:23.120
Cahn's

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:26.270
YouTube channel. So I

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.589
encourage everybody to watch that; that

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:29.270
was a real blessing. It blessed me; I

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.470
could feel the presence of the Lord. It

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.949
made me want to weep because people were

00:02:33.959 --> 00:02:36.150
crying out for

00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:38.150
repentance,

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.550
seeking the Lord, and this is what it's

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:43.270
going to take for revival. If my people,

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:45.910
who are called by my name, will humble

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:48.149
themselves and pray and turn from their

00:02:48.159 --> 00:02:51.070
wicked ways,

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:58.390
He said

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:00.070
we would hear from heaven and He would heal

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:01.070
our

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.509
land. I believe that God is not done

00:03:04.519 --> 00:03:07.710
with America yet, that there is one last

00:03:07.720 --> 00:03:10.509
revival that will take place. He said,

00:03:10.519 --> 00:03:13.149
"Brandon, there will be a shaking

00:03:13.149 --> 00:03:13.159
to awaken,"and

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:15.350
whatever it takes, His remnant

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.750
right now is preparing themselves. We're

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:20.030
ready, and we're getting our hearts ready

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.110
before Him right now as the

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:24.869
glorious church ready for a great

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:27.910
revival. I believe with all my heart

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:29.830
we're about to see the

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:32.750
demonstrations and manifestations of the

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:35.869
glory of God like we've never seen

00:03:35.879 --> 00:03:38.789
before. Like He said to me, "Brandon,

00:03:38.799 --> 00:03:41.630
the old wells are becoming

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:43.429
uncapped, and we're going

00:03:43.439 --> 00:03:46.149
to go down to the deep

00:03:46.149 --> 00:03:46.159
parts."People

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:48.509
say, "Well, we want to go back

00:03:48.519 --> 00:03:49.789
and just see those old

00:03:49.789 --> 00:03:49.799
revivals."No,

00:03:49.799 --> 00:03:52.869
I want something new,

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:55.429
something

00:03:55.429 --> 00:03:55.439
fresh—a

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:57.470
new, fresh experience of the presence of

00:03:57.480 --> 00:04:00.509
the Lord, not the old thing. Let's do

00:04:00.519 --> 00:04:04.110
something new. So I'm

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:07.309
excited for what the Lord is about to do.

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:10.869
The old revivals, the old

00:04:10.879 --> 00:04:14.869
Harbinger Church,

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:21.189
the old tent revivals, the

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:25.230
old outpouring like it was at

00:04:25.230 --> 00:04:25.240
Azusa—I

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:27.150
believe that we'll see something

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:29.710
greater: the former and latter

00:04:29.710 --> 00:04:29.720
rain

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:32.070
together in a greater way in

00:04:32.070 --> 00:04:32.080
these

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:35.430
last seconds of these last hours.

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:39.310
This is a

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:41.590
pillow my wife put on there

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.790
so you all could see it. I got this at

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:47.469
Nancy DeFrain's healing thing she did at

00:04:47.479 --> 00:04:49.990
the church, and this is Jesus the Healer.

