What a witness and a

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:54.870
testimony of who Jesus is and

00:04:54.880 --> 00:04:57.469
what He does for the body of Christ to

00:04:57.479 --> 00:04:58.909
wear. You could probably get

00:04:58.919 --> 00:05:00.310
that on her

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:03.310
