00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.430
see it. It has an eagle on the front, too.

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:17.629
I thought that was pretty cool.

00:05:17.639 --> 00:05:19.550
I just love the witness of it because

00:05:19.560 --> 00:05:21.510
it's who I am. I believe it with all

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:24.469
my heart that Jesus is a healer, and so I

00:05:24.479 --> 00:05:27.430
said, "That's perfect, I'll wear

00:05:27.430 --> 00:05:27.440
it."I

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:30.390
was excited she got that for me.

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:32.870
So I just want to

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:36.390
encourage you all today about the

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:38.990
visitations and the manifestations of

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:41.029
angelic

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:43.749
encounters. I believe what the Lord

00:05:43.759 --> 00:05:45.870
showed me—He said,

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:47.510
"As you're

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:49.670
