00:05:53.280 --> 00:05:55.870
more angelic visitations than you've

00:05:55.880 --> 00:05:57.629
ever experienced before,

00:05:57.629 --> 00:05:57.639
Brandon."And

00:05:57.639 --> 00:06:00.909
it has been so. I've

00:06:00.919 --> 00:06:03.390
had a lot of encounters from angelic

00:06:03.400 --> 00:06:07.189
help and divine protection.

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:09.550
I've seen secret service angels.

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:11.070
The Lord shows me these things, and I'm

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:12.830
excited about it. But He told me,

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:14.870
"I want you to go on and encourage

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:19.749
my people today about expecting divine

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:23.950
protection, expecting divine

00:06:23.950 --> 00:06:23.960
whatever."I

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:26.110
mean, whatever you need, the

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:28.830
Lord has it. I believe with all my

00:06:28.840 --> 00:06:31.350
heart we're in a time like never before.

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.629
We're going to see things like we've

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:35.350
