00:06:38.520 --> 00:06:40.870
on this for just a

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:40.880
second—I'll

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:42.790
give you one or two of them and then

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:44.629
we'll pray—but I just want to encourage

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:47.510
