00:11:44.110 --> 00:11:44.120
C-word

00:11:44.120 --> 00:11:47.829
shot; You

00:11:47.839 --> 00:11:51.949
have it all. You cover us, and I believe

00:11:51.959 --> 00:11:55.310
that You are my protector, that no weapon,

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:58.750
no pestilence, no plague comes nigh me. I

00:11:58.760 --> 00:12:00.670
take this, Father, and I thank You, Lord;

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:03.430
this is my Holy Ghost

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:06.350
vaccination. Lord, I thank You for

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:09.389
Your protection over me. You have

00:12:09.399 --> 00:12:13.870
been

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.269
good, and Your

00:12:15.279 --> 00:12:18.230
mercy is new every

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:22.949
morning; Your mercy endures

00:12:22.959 --> 00:12:26.269
forever. Thank You, Father.

00:12:31.959 --> 00:12:33.629
Now, Lord, we take the

00:12:33.639 --> 00:12:36.509
blood. We thank You for Your blood, Lord,

00:12:36.519 --> 00:12:40.629
that all our sins are washed

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:43.150
away. It is by the blood of the Lamb and by the

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:46.230
word of our

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:49.750
testimony. It's a holy thing. We don't

00:12:49.760 --> 00:12:53.710
flippantly

00:12:53.720 --> 00:12:56.550
do it, but we do it with all our

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:59.350
heart.

00:12:59.350 --> 00:12:59.360
Jesus'blood

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:03.750
was shed for me, it was

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:06.629
shed for them, and I thank You for Your

00:13:06.639 --> 00:13:10.110
blood. I thank You for the cross. I thank

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:12.710
You for washing over me. The blood of

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:15.509
Jesus washes me, and You watch over me,

00:13:15.519 --> 00:13:16.910
my children,

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:16.920
and

00:13:16.920 --> 00:13:19.030
my wife. Father, I thank You for

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:20.750
the protection of Your

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:25.470
blood. We make much of the blood,

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:28.629
and the blood makes much of us. We

00:13:28.639 --> 00:13:30.750
take this blood right now in the name of

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:35.230
Jesus. Thank You,

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:37.550
Lord,

00:13:37.560 --> 00:13:39.990
that You atoned

00:13:39.990 --> 00:13:40.000
for

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:42.110
our

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:45.670
sins; You don't even remember

00:13:45.670 --> 00:13:45.680
them.

00:13:45.680 --> 00:13:47.310
Thank You, Lord,

00:13:47.320 --> 00:13:49.790
for Your mercy, for

00:13:49.800 --> 00:13:52.189
healing

00:13:52.199 --> 00:13:54.749
us by

00:13:54.759 --> 00:13:58.590
the covenant You gave to

00:13:58.600 --> 00:13:59.710
us.

00:13:59.720 --> 00:14:01.790
Greater works will we

00:14:01.800 --> 00:14:04.590
do because You went to the Father

00:14:04.590 --> 00:14:04.600
and

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:08.310
sent us

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:11.790
the Comforter, the

00:14:11.800 --> 00:14:15.230
Holy Spirit, who dwells on the inside

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:18.189
of us. Holy

00:14:18.199 --> 00:14:21.829
Spirit, we invite You into this

00:14:21.839 --> 00:14:25.350
time.

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:28.430
Thank You for this day, for this is

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:31.550
the day the Lord has made and we will

00:14:31.560 --> 00:14:35.150
rejoice and be glad in

00:14:35.160 --> 00:14:37.150
it.

00:14:39.560 --> 00:14:41.949
We want

00:14:41.959 --> 00:14:43.870
You

00:14:43.880 --> 00:14:47.910
to be our friend, our standby, our helper.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:49.590
You said You would teach us and guide us

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:53.389
into all things.

00:14:57.720 --> 00:15:00.430
Whatever it is, You have

00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:04.030
the answer. We do not

00:15:04.040 --> 00:15:06.910
lean on our own intellect—because

00:15:06.910 --> 00:15:06.920
that would

00:15:06.920 --> 00:15:09.990
be really bad for

00:15:09.990 --> 00:15:10.000
me—but

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:11.870
Lord, I thank

00:15:11.880 --> 00:15:14.749
You that we have the mind of

00:15:14.759 --> 00:15:22.710
Christ.

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:25.269
I thank You that You're

00:15:25.279 --> 00:15:26.829
the

00:15:26.839 --> 00:15:29.470
captain, and I'm not even the

00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:29.480
co-captain,

00:15:29.480 --> 00:15:31.470
Lord; I just sit in the back and let You

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.670
steer the

00:15:32.680 --> 00:15:37.309
ship in every area of my life.

00:15:42.519 --> 00:15:44.150
Father, I thank You that You have a

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:47.910
perfect plan for

00:15:47.920 --> 00:15:51.670
us—perfect

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:55.189
peace, perfect

00:15:55.189 --> 00:15:55.199
everything—because

00:15:55.199 --> 00:15:56.910
we're allowing You to

00:15:56.920 --> 00:15:59.910
steer our lives.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.590
You said, "Trust in the Lord with all your

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:04.670
heart, and lean not unto your own

00:16:04.680 --> 00:16:07.269
understanding, but in all your ways

00:16:07.279 --> 00:16:09.509
acknowledge Him, and He shall

00:16:09.509 --> 00:16:09.519
direct

00:16:09.519 --> 00:16:13.949
your

00:16:13.949 --> 00:16:13.959
paths."We

00:16:13.959 --> 00:16:19.110
trust You, Lord. We let go.

00:16:26.839 --> 00:16:29.110
It may not make any sense at all,

00:16:31.959 --> 00:16:34.790
but it

00:16:34.790 --> 00:16:34.800
doesn't

00:16:34.800 --> 00:16:36.230
have to when you're

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:37.590
trusting

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:42.389
Jesus. We

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:44.550
reach forth and grab onto the new

00:16:44.560 --> 00:16:46.550
thing, letting go of the

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:49.749
past. I'm not going to keep

00:16:49.759 --> 00:16:52.629
looking back over my shoulder; I press

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:56.069
on for You, Jesus, and look for the

00:16:56.079 --> 00:16:58.350
fresh things.

00:17:00.360 --> 00:17:03.590
God has

00:17:03.600 --> 00:17:06.510
our future.

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:11.510
"Beloved, I wish above all things that thou

00:17:11.510 --> 00:17:11.520
mayest

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:14.949
prosper and be in health, even as

00:17:14.949 --> 00:17:14.959
thy

00:17:14.959 --> 00:17:16.870
soul

00:17:16.870 --> 00:17:16.880
prospers."So

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:19.309
I'm going to talk to you all

00:17:19.319 --> 00:17:22.029
about angelic

00:17:22.039 --> 00:17:23.590
visitations.

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:27.350
One night, my wife and I were lying

00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:29.789
in bed asleep, probably

00:17:29.799 --> 00:17:32.510
about 4:00 in the morning, and all of

00:17:32.520 --> 00:17:36.070
a sudden we felt our whole roof shake.

00:17:36.080 --> 00:17:37.870
I thought somebody was breaking in.

00:17:37.880 --> 00:17:41.590
It was so

00:17:41.600 --> 00:17:44.470
strong that it

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:46.710
literally felt like something was coming

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:49.310
through.

00:17:49.320 --> 00:17:52.909
It woke us both up. I

00:17:52.919 --> 00:17:55.270
flew out of bed, turned on

00:17:55.280 --> 00:17:57.549
the light, grabbed my firearm, and

00:17:57.559 --> 00:18:01.590
was going toward the door

00:18:01.590 --> 00:18:01.600
when

00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:04.029
instantaneously my eyes were

00:18:04.029 --> 00:18:04.039
translated

00:18:04.039 --> 00:18:05.630
over to the realm of the spirit.

00:18:05.640 --> 00:18:08.470
The Lord allowed

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:12.789
me to see these three massive

00:18:12.789 --> 00:18:12.799
pig-looking

00:18:12.799 --> 00:18:16.149
demons with long evil noses

00:18:16.159 --> 00:18:18.750
and eyes that were red and

00:18:18.760 --> 00:18:21.750
slanted. They had scaly skin

00:18:23.590 --> 00:18:23.600
and

00:18:25.799 --> 00:18:29.270
long nasty

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:29.280
hair—of

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:31.990
course, it's

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:34.310
a demon.

00:18:34.320 --> 00:18:38.230
One was like a black mist

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:40.669
or

00:18:40.679 --> 00:18:43.110
a fog

00:18:43.110 --> 00:18:43.120
that

00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:45.430
you could see

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:49.029
through, but it had evil red

00:18:49.039 --> 00:18:51.630
eyes. The other one looked like a

00:18:53.600 --> 00:18:54.909
pig, and the

00:18:54.909 --> 00:18:54.919
third

00:18:54.919 --> 00:18:57.870
one was red and

00:18:57.880 --> 00:19:00.190
very gnarly-looking with big black horns.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.710
It looked like something off of

00:19:01.710 --> 00:19:01.720
A

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:04.789
Witch's Invitation with

00:19:04.789 --> 00:19:04.799
Carman.

00:19:04.799 --> 00:19:07.390
They were hissing and growling, but

00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:10.630
they couldn't get close to the

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:13.390
house. It's like they were being blocked.

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:18.230
I know I

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:20.149
put a bloodline around my home,

00:19:20.159 --> 00:19:24.669
but at this time I was just staring

00:19:24.679 --> 00:19:26.270
at

00:19:26.280 --> 00:19:28.430
them.

00:19:28.440 --> 00:19:30.669
It was like when you see a bull scrape the dirt; they were

00:19:30.679 --> 00:19:32.510
scraping the dirt like they were trying

00:19:32.520 --> 00:19:35.669
to get traction to come

00:19:35.679 --> 00:19:38.789
at me, but they couldn't. All of a

00:19:38.799 --> 00:19:41.870
sudden, I see these massive

00:19:41.880 --> 00:19:44.029
angelic

00:19:44.039 --> 00:19:47.830
beings. They were massive, and they

00:19:47.840 --> 00:19:50.190
had their arms

00:19:52.120 --> 00:19:53.830
interlocked—they

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:56.710
had their hands on their

00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:58.789
hips

00:19:58.799 --> 00:20:00.510
and

00:20:00.520 --> 00:20:02.630
were locked together. I believe

00:20:02.640 --> 00:20:04.750
there were three or four of

00:20:04.760 --> 00:20:07.310
them. They

00:20:07.320 --> 00:20:09.270
were standing up, and I bet they were

00:20:09.270 --> 00:20:09.280
seventeen

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:12.710
feet

00:20:12.710 --> 00:20:12.720
high—massive,

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:14.950
bigger than my tree out

00:20:14.950 --> 00:20:14.960
front—and

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:18.390
they were wide.

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:22.470
They were glowing with

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:26.630
glory. When I looked over and

00:20:26.630 --> 00:20:26.640
saw

00:20:26.640 --> 00:20:29.190
them protecting me,

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.630
they didn't have swords

00:20:31.640 --> 00:20:33.149
or

00:20:33.159 --> 00:20:36.350
shields; they were just a wall. They had

00:20:36.350 --> 00:20:36.360
these

00:20:36.360 --> 00:20:39.590
beautiful gowns on,

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:42.149
and

00:20:42.159 --> 00:20:44.830
their voices were like

00:20:44.840 --> 00:20:48.350
thunder when they spoke.

00:20:48.360 --> 00:20:50.950
It sounded

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:54.870
like a

00:20:54.880 --> 00:20:57.710
thunderous echo.

00:21:01.240 --> 00:21:04.789
When I saw them standing there,

00:21:07.280 --> 00:21:12.269
I said, "Praise the

00:21:12.269 --> 00:21:12.279
Lord!"And

00:21:12.279 --> 00:21:14.909
when I said that, they

00:21:14.919 --> 00:21:17.350
turned back and looked at me and

00:21:17.360 --> 00:21:19.230
said,

00:21:19.240 --> 00:21:22.549
"Praise the Lord!"They started

00:21:22.559 --> 00:21:26.630
worshiping the Lord with me.

00:21:36.279 --> 00:21:38.830
Every single time they said "Praise

00:21:38.840 --> 00:21:41.269
the Lord,"it echoed throughout the neighborhood.

00:21:41.269 --> 00:21:41.279
It wasn't

00:21:41.279 --> 00:21:43.870
in the

00:21:43.870 --> 00:21:43.880
natural; it

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:46.029
was

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:56.750
the spirit.

00:21:56.760 --> 00:21:59.029
I want to tell you all:

00:21:59.039 --> 00:22:00.909
the spirit realm is more real than

00:22:05.240 --> 00:22:08.029
the natural realm. It's just one

00:22:08.039 --> 00:22:10.830
breath away.

00:22:10.840 --> 00:22:13.430
To be absent from the

00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:15.669
body is to be present with the Lord.

00:22:15.679 --> 00:22:19.310
Instantaneously, we go into the spirit

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:27.390
realm, and the

00:22:37.400 --> 00:22:41.590
angels

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:44.549
were crying, "Praise the

00:22:44.549 --> 00:22:44.559
Lord!"At

00:22:44.559 --> 00:22:47.190
this time, I see a

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.950
portal open over to the east,

00:22:50.960 --> 00:22:55.310
and I can see into the glory, into the

00:22:55.320 --> 00:22:57.630
heavens.

00:22:57.640 --> 00:23:00.669
There was light up there, and

00:23:00.679 --> 00:23:02.669
you could see the holy city.

00:23:15.320 --> 00:23:17.830
All of a sudden, when they said "Praise

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:20.990
the Lord,"that light from heaven—the

00:23:20.990 --> 00:23:21.000
glory—shined

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.950
down on

00:23:23.960 --> 00:23:27.269
those angels and made them

00:23:27.279 --> 00:23:30.510
glow.

00:23:39.990 --> 00:23:40.000
They

00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:51.510
started glowing with the

00:23:51.520 --> 00:23:54.230
glory, and their

00:23:54.230 --> 00:23:54.240
faces

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:58.750
shined. I said,

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:01.990
"Holy, holy, holy is the Lord!"and they said,

00:24:02.000 --> 00:24:05.710
"Holy, holy, holy is the

00:24:05.710 --> 00:24:05.720
Lord!"You

00:24:05.720 --> 00:24:08.549
could hear it

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:18.750
through the

00:24:18.760 --> 00:24:21.510
atmosphere. I stood

00:24:21.520 --> 00:24:23.590
there and watched this

00:24:23.600 --> 00:24:27.070
for a long time because

00:24:31.799 --> 00:24:36.070
it was

00:24:36.080 --> 00:24:39.430
beautiful. As I was

00:24:39.440 --> 00:24:43.110
worshiping, they worshiped with

00:24:43.120 --> 00:24:46.149
me, and I didn't even pay attention to

00:24:46.159 --> 00:24:47.750
the devils anymore.

00:24:47.760 --> 00:24:50.470
They went away as we

00:24:50.480 --> 00:24:53.230
worshiped.

00:24:53.240 --> 00:24:56.149
I was so fixed on those

00:24:56.159 --> 00:24:59.230
angelic beings that I had

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:01.710
completely forgotten the devils

00:25:01.720 --> 00:25:04.269
were there. When I looked back down,

00:25:04.279 --> 00:25:06.789
they

00:25:06.799 --> 00:25:08.950
were

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:11.789
gone. I guess they got scared

00:25:11.799 --> 00:25:15.110
away. But I want to tell you, your

00:25:15.120 --> 00:25:17.830
angels keep charge over you. Psalm

00:25:17.830 --> 00:25:17.840
91 says

00:25:17.840 --> 00:25:19.190
they would bear us up in their

00:25:19.200 --> 00:25:21.430
hands lest we dash our foot

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:25.029
against a stone. I believe with

00:25:25.039 --> 00:25:27.990
all my heart that's

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:29.389
happening all the time and we don't

00:25:29.399 --> 00:25:32.269
even know it.

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:39.710
Well, I went to work the next day at the

00:25:39.720 --> 00:25:42.310
church.

00:25:46.679 --> 00:25:50.350
I was so excited because we had a staff meeting. I told the pastor the whole thing, and he said, "Brandon, I don't doubt it. I actually see a glow on your face."The holy glow was still shining on me. He said he could see a tangible manifestation of the spirit of the Lord on my face. That visitation changed my life. I learned how to deal with stuff in the spirit realm more and more. It's like trial and error—one day at a time. Nobody really ever mentored me. I used to think you had to be friends with upper leadership or rub shoulders with them to get your call. You go to conferences and want to sit on the front row so they'll notice you and give you a prophecy. I realized I went to all the revivals and worked for mega-churches, putting myself in a position to be seen because I knew God had a call on me. I

00:25:50.360 --> 00:25:53.269
wanted any guest speaker or prophet to see me on the front row. How many times did I wait in the back room just to say hi to the pastor? But the more I pushed for it, the more they looked at me and said, "We don't see it. In fact, we see you're a janitor."And I kept cleaning. I had certain dear people who would see it, and big ministers who laid hands on me, but I'd always come back

00:25:53.269 --> 00:25:53.279
and quote them: "So-and-so said this about me."It gave me just enough encouragement to keep going. But

00:25:53.279 --> 00:25:55.029
you don't need to rub shoulders with your pastor for your call to come to pass. Now I sit in the back row a lot. I don't need them to tip their hat toward me; Jesus tipped His hat toward me and said, "Start a YouTube channel."What He's done has been amazing, and nobody else can take the glory for it. It was always Jesus. You don't have to have man promote you. He said to me, "Brandon, you cannot earn the anointing; you qualify for it.

00:25:55.029 --> 00:25:55.039
I will equip the qualified."Many in the body try to earn it by giving money or doing things, but there's nothing you can

00:25:55.039 --> 00:25:57.070
do other than be obedient—walking in His glory and dying to self daily. The Apostle Paul said, "I die daily."So I want to encourage you: you don't need a Reinhard Bonnke or somebody to acknowledge the gift on your life. Seek Jesus with your whole heart, and He'll bring it to pass. I deliberately sit in the back because I don't need that. It was heartbreaking; I went for fifteen years as just the guy in the bathroom. I cleaned with all my heart—scrubbing the cracks and the grout—and it wasn't always easy.

00:25:57.070 --> 00:25:57.080
In that process of cleaning up vomit and diarrhea year after

00:25:57.080 --> 00:25:59.430
year, setting up chairs in the sanctuary, I learned a lot

00:25:59.430 --> 00:25:59.440
about the mega-church world. It's a lot of racket and insecurity,

00:25:59.440 --> 00:26:02.350
but it's all

00:26:02.350 --> 00:26:02.360
about Jesus.

00:26:02.360 --> 00:26:04.710
Don't give up on your dream just because somebody doesn't acknowledge you. Jesus acknowledges

00:26:04.710 --> 00:26:04.720
you. Don't despise small beginnings. Volunteering to clean bathrooms—Jesus loves it. The greatest

00:26:04.720 --> 00:26:06.269
visitations I've ever had were behind a commode. Seriously, cleaning out feminine trash cans—those

00:26:06.269 --> 00:26:06.279
are some of the most precious memories I have. He became beautiful in

00:26:06.279 --> 00:26:08.269
my life during the hard times.

00:26:08.269 --> 00:26:08.279
If you lean not unto

00:26:08.279 --> 00:26:11.070
your own

00:26:11.070 --> 00:26:11.080
understanding,

00:26:11.080 --> 00:26:13.190
the

00:26:13.200 --> 00:26:15.830
Lord said to put gasoline on their fire, son,

00:26:15.840 --> 00:26:19.149
and fan

00:26:19.149 --> 00:26:19.159
them, and

